    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm not saying i want to hurt myself or anything, i'm just being realistic. it's just a logical thing. when someone is a constant drain on everyone they love, and there's no way to fix it, isn't it just more of a kindness to stop being the problem? it feels more like a way to fix it than a way to break it.",
